      <h2 id="faq">Frequently asked questions</h2>
      <div class="two-col">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>What do you need from us?</h3>
          <p>Basic business details, problem statement, solution outline, supplier quotes or shortlists, and any prior drafts. We provide templates to speed this up.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Do you help with suppliers?</h3>
